1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,862
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:13,759
Mom,

4
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:17,559
I'll never let Jiang Xiao go.

5
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,160
By the way,

6
00:00:24,679 --> 00:00:26,719
these are all the evidence
of Jiang Xiao's crimes.

7
00:00:27,719 --> 00:00:28,920
Zechen told me that as long

8
00:00:29,239 --> 00:00:30,879
as I hand them over to you,

9
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,600
you will know what to do.

10
00:00:35,719 --> 00:00:36,719
It is time

11
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:41,000
for Jiang Xiao to experience
the force of a storm.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,799
Mom,

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,520
I'm heading out for a while.

14
00:00:53,799 --> 00:00:55,240
Get some rest early.

15
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,079
Alright.

16
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,000
Nian.

17
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:06,519
Qiao Nian.

18
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:11,280
I'll have to trouble you
to look after my mother.

19
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:12,239
Don't worry.

20
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:13,519
Leave it to us.

21
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:14,550
Thank you.

22
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:15,349
Mhm.

23
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,719
Be careful!

24
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,920
Ms. Qiao, Mr. Jiang Zechen
sent me to pick you up.

25
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,159
Alright.

26
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:37,120
Miss Qiao, I'm sorry.

27
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:40,159
What are you doing?
Let go of me! Let go!

28
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,799
Take Ms. Xie away, quickly!

29
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,519
Alright.

30
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,239
Ms. Xie, come with me.

31
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,040
- What's happening?
- Hurry up!

32
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,159
Go!

33
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,080
Alright.

34
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,560
Move!

35
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:15,039
Where do you think you're going?

36
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,319
(Who is it?)

37
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:29,599
(Who exactly tied me up here?)

38
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,400
Who are you?

39
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:35,439
Show yourself if you dare!

40
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,639
Zechen?

41
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,560
Zechen, you came to save me?

42
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,000
Zechen.

43
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,479
Zechen.

44
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,080
The chip is inside the ring.

45
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,520
I secretly hid it
beneath the wooden board.

46
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,120
Zechen...

47
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,719
What does this mean?

48
00:03:49,450 --> 00:03:50,730
I forgot to tell you.

49
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,919
Never trust others so easily.

50
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,439
Jiang Zechen.

51
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,360
So you've been deceiving me all along.

52
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,800
Jiang Zechen,

53
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,560
what are you trying to do?

54
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,839
Jiang Zechen!

55
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,000
Jiang Zechen.

56
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,639
Do you want money? Power?

57
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,040
Or the entire group?

58
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,560
I can give you everything.

59
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,800
Why must you do this?

60
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:36,240
Were all those years of marriage

61
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,199
nothing but a lie?

62
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,000
Shut up!

63
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,199
Everything you speak of,

64
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,199
only becomes truly mine

65
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,920
once you are no longer here!

66
00:04:49,712 --> 00:04:55,725
♪Our meeting, like the wind,
part truth, part dream♪

67
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,600
Jiang Zechen...

68
00:04:56,675 --> 00:04:57,840
♪After our clash, we're lost♪

69
00:04:57,840 --> 00:05:00,839
♪In a labyrinth of bewildered gazes♪

70
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:03,240
Jiang Zechen!

71
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:09,720
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

72
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:12,040
Jiang Zechen!

73
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,079
Jiang Zechen!

74
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:20,120
Jiang Zechen!

75
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,639
Jiang Zechen!

76
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,720
Are you going to kill me?

77
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:29,800
Help! Someone help!

78
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,639
Help!

79
00:05:33,763 --> 00:05:38,100
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

80
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,600
(I gained everything,)

81
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:44,199
(yet lost you.)

82
00:05:45,563 --> 00:05:49,050
♪Yet I still want you close♪

83
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:53,213
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

84
00:05:53,213 --> 00:05:56,079
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

85
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:58,680
Jiang Zechen, I hate you!

86
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:07,403
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

87
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,240
My dear son,

88
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:31,959
from now on, everything
in Qiao family will belong to us.

89
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,680
Hand it over.

90
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:44,360
What about the 50%
shares of the Qiao Group

91
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,360
and Zemu's ashes?

92
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,240
Why the hurry?

93
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:51,199
Zemu's ashes are in my study.

94
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,399
With them in my possession,

95
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:59,160
Qiao Group will cease to exist.

96
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,959
Once everything is settled,

97
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:03,680
I will naturally give you what is yours.

98
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,680
Check it.

99
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,240
Well done, my son.

100
00:07:18,237 --> 00:07:19,562
（LOADING）

101
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,237
（INITIALIZATION）

102
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,480
Mr. Jiang, look,

103
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,839
the chip contains a virus.

104
00:07:27,787 --> 00:07:29,762
（INITIALIZATION）

105
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:45,079
Fine. You dare to deceive me?

106
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:47,920
Jiang Zechen! Go after him!

107
00:07:51,262 --> 00:07:54,162
(Three Days Earlier)

108
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,360
Jiang Xiao... he!

109
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,439
Shh.

110
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:18,079
This is... a bug?

111
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,440
It's my mom.

112
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,039
It's my mom...

113
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,720
It really is my mom.

114
00:09:02,010 --> 00:09:07,980
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

115
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:15,860
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

116
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:19,700
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

117
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:23,500
♪Where this ends♪

118
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:30,780
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

119
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:35,110
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

120
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:38,230
♪Love turns into pain♪

121
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:42,420
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

122
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:46,060
♪Yet I still want you close♪

123
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:50,230
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

124
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:53,540
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

125
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:58,110
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

126
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:04,420
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

